name: craig threlkeld
text: Look, is this as good as you can make from scratch (if you can cook)? No, it isn't, but is it better than any frozen pizza and most delivery pizzas I've eaten? It sure is. …More

text: Ordered a pizza at 8:25pm went to pick up at 8:45pm and the doors were locked. I called and a woman said they were "doing construction next door" and had to close down early. Funny cause there was no sign on the door and no lights on next …More

name: Clayton Riley
text: I love Chicago Stuffed Pizza and this location makes it the best. The ingredients are always spread perfectly and the crust isnt smashed down. Staff is always super polite and quick.

name: Ian Herron
text: Tried to roll by to take advantage of their tuesday deal and its gone, no signs no forward address just ghosted, did i miss something? Or did it just suprise shut down?

name: David D
text: Good pizza. The wait time here is usually spot on. The cost is a bit more than the value, but if you get a coupon or check out their daily specials you’ll save a bit more. Overall, I’d recommend this place.

name: Mads R
text: My family and I are long time patrons (since the store first opened) and we are severely disappointed with the quality of service as time has gone by. In particular, it is nigh impossible to order over the phone, as I've tried 21 times to …More

name: George Graves
text: I love making my own pizza! Sometimes they have great deals

name: Cynthia
text: They'll make you any kind of pizza you want or you can select from their option menu. You take the pizza home and bake "cook" it.

name: C S
text: Quality has become highly variable recently. The store needs better management so they don't run out of something before 530 PM.

name: Tim Hunt
text: There are lots of pizza options and i think we can all agree that there are better (and more expensive) options than Papa Murphy's - but overall this place is great for what it is.  Seems to be staffed by younger (highschool/college) kids …More

text: Consistently good pizza and always a bargain

name: Kimberly Poole
text: Better than frozen and also better than some delivery.

name: Adam Jones
text: Consistent pizzas! Parking can suck.

name: Daniel L
text: Sat on hold forever!!!  This is why there are dying businesses in West Seattle.  I was reading reviews about how the employees at Papa Murphys REALLY like that hold button while I was on hold.  Kind of ironic.  Get it together!

name: Lauri Robinson
text: We take 2 buses just to come to this Papa Murphy's. The team there is exceptional. No other pizza compares.

name: Chris Rogge
text: This is my favorite Papa Murphy's !!   They make the best pizzas ever !!! I have never been disappointed with my pizza.  They have wonderful customer service and always smiling!
